1
00:01:32,150 --> 00:01:39,970
[Better Halves]

2
00:01:40,200 --> 00:01:42,930
[Episode 22]

3
00:01:43,570 --> 00:01:45,000
Once the supplies arrive,

4
00:01:45,000 --> 00:01:46,979
we'll have a long battle with them.

5
00:01:47,380 --> 00:01:48,550
Even if we can't defeat them,

6
00:01:48,550 --> 00:01:50,150
we'll have to wear them down.

7
00:01:50,370 --> 00:01:52,070
But I'm worried that

8
00:01:52,100 --> 00:01:53,220
if this lasts too long,

9
00:01:53,220 --> 00:01:54,870
we might not be able to hang on.

10
00:01:54,870 --> 00:01:55,820
Don't worry.

11
00:01:55,850 --> 00:01:57,550
We certainly won't just sit there
waiting for death.

12
00:01:57,550 --> 00:01:58,440
Zhuxi.

13
00:01:58,710 --> 00:02:01,020
I've just thought of a plan

14
00:02:01,390 --> 00:02:03,980
that can dampen their spirits.

15
00:02:07,140 --> 00:02:08,460
Our army is greatly outnumbered.

16
00:02:08,460 --> 00:02:09,470
We need to fully utilize

17
00:02:09,470 --> 00:02:10,940
the terrain advantages of Mount Qianya.

18
00:02:10,940 --> 00:02:12,110
The eastern terrain is flat,

19
00:02:12,110 --> 00:02:12,790
which is unfavorable for us.

20
00:02:12,790 --> 00:02:13,460
Hurry up!

21
00:02:13,480 --> 00:02:15,480
Take a team and set up an ambush here.

22
00:02:15,520 --> 00:02:16,090
Shoot the arrows!

23
00:02:16,090 --> 00:02:17,150
Pretend to attack.

24
00:02:25,850 --> 00:02:27,380
Then just fake a retreat from a defeat

25
00:02:27,380 --> 00:02:29,640
and lure them beneath the western cliff.

26
00:02:31,020 --> 00:02:31,770
Retreat!

27
00:02:34,130 --> 00:02:34,790
Chase them!

28
00:02:35,020 --> 00:02:35,460
Yes!

29
00:02:36,000 --> 00:02:37,200
-Let's go!
-Let's go!

30
00:02:39,860 --> 00:02:41,500
The rest of you
should fight the enmey with me

31
00:02:41,500 --> 00:02:44,230
and set up an ambush
at the western mountain pass.

32
00:02:53,660 --> 00:02:54,690
Shoot!

33
00:03:21,230 --> 00:03:21,910
Shoot the arrows!

34
00:03:21,910 --> 00:03:24,510
Everyone,
aim carefully and shoot the arrows!

35
00:04:54,020 --> 00:04:55,780
Retreat! Hurry up!

36
00:05:00,310 --> 00:05:01,520
Chi.

37
00:05:13,670 --> 00:05:14,920
Ke has been arrested.

38
00:05:15,310 --> 00:05:17,240
Is there no justice in the capital now?

39
00:05:17,240 --> 00:05:18,120
I'm going to reason with them.

40
00:05:18,120 --> 00:05:18,460
Let's go!

41
00:05:18,460 --> 00:05:20,140
Kexian, calm down.

42
00:05:20,360 --> 00:05:21,790
They arrested her without any evidence.

43
00:05:21,790 --> 00:05:23,490
Do you think they'll listen to the reason?

44
00:05:23,490 --> 00:05:25,620
I've sent a letter to Chief about this.

45
00:05:25,820 --> 00:05:26,740
However,

46
00:05:27,050 --> 00:05:28,180
the journey is long.

47
00:05:29,580 --> 00:05:31,230
In the Military Headquarters Prison,

48
00:05:31,230 --> 00:05:33,490
I don't know whether Ke can hang in there.

49
00:05:35,040 --> 00:05:36,600
I'm going to
the Military Headquarters now.

50
00:05:36,600 --> 00:05:37,840
If they dare to give Ke a hard time,

51
00:05:37,840 --> 00:05:38,890
I'll take her out of there forcibly.

52
00:05:38,890 --> 00:05:40,050
-Calm down.
-Xianxian!

53
00:05:40,050 --> 00:05:41,630
Your parents and Qin'er are still at home.

54
00:05:41,630 --> 00:05:43,360
If you're so reckless,
not only will you be unable to save her,

55
00:05:43,360 --> 00:05:45,080
but you'll also get yourself into trouble.

56
00:05:45,080 --> 00:05:47,409
Won't that make everyone worry about you?

57
00:05:48,409 --> 00:05:49,460
Everyone, please calm down.

58
00:05:49,460 --> 00:05:50,790
Let's think clearly first.

59
00:05:50,790 --> 00:05:52,220
They clearly came prepared,

60
00:05:52,220 --> 00:05:53,480
and they outnumber us.

61
00:05:53,500 --> 00:05:55,880
We can't use force.
We can only use our wits.

62
00:05:55,880 --> 00:05:58,159
The Military Headquarters
is abusing its power like this.

63
00:05:58,159 --> 00:05:59,710
But they still have to be reasonable.

64
00:05:59,710 --> 00:06:02,820
If we can also put some pressure on them,

65
00:06:03,060 --> 00:06:04,660
perhaps there's still hope.

66
00:06:04,770 --> 00:06:06,370
Even if Ke can't be released,

67
00:06:06,480 --> 00:06:08,710
we can at least ensure
that her life won't be in danger.

68
00:06:08,710 --> 00:06:09,570
How about this?

69
00:06:10,060 --> 00:06:12,140
I'll go to the magistrate's office
to see Lord Zheng

70
00:06:12,140 --> 00:06:14,240
and ask him to smooth things out
at the Military Headquarters.

71
00:06:14,240 --> 00:06:15,150
That's a good idea.

72
00:06:15,150 --> 00:06:15,830
Let's go.

73
00:06:15,850 --> 00:06:16,630
That's not enough.

74
00:06:16,630 --> 00:06:18,880
That lieutenant said
he came here under the imperial decree.

75
00:06:18,880 --> 00:06:20,490
If someone really gave the order,

76
00:06:20,490 --> 00:06:23,840
I'm afraid even the magistrate's office
has no authority to intervene.

77
00:06:23,840 --> 00:06:25,260
What should we do then?

78
00:06:26,510 --> 00:06:27,870
If we can gather

79
00:06:27,900 --> 00:06:29,470
all of Ke's former clients

80
00:06:29,500 --> 00:06:31,030
and ask them
to intercede for her together,

81
00:06:31,030 --> 00:06:32,960
Ke might be able to be released

82
00:06:32,980 --> 00:06:35,240
from the Military Headquarters Prison.

83
00:06:35,570 --> 00:06:37,280
We need someone with prestige

84
00:06:37,300 --> 00:06:38,770
to help us now.

85
00:06:38,970 --> 00:06:39,930
Miss Cheng.

86
00:06:40,260 --> 00:06:41,860
Miss Cheng from Jiangning's Dream

87
00:06:41,860 --> 00:06:43,430
is His Majesty's sworn sister.

88
00:06:43,430 --> 00:06:44,310
In addition,

89
00:06:44,810 --> 00:06:46,520
Xu Ao,
Commander of the Imperial Cavalry Bureau,

90
00:06:46,520 --> 00:06:47,760
is His Majesty's internal official.

91
00:06:47,760 --> 00:06:49,260
One of them
is a member of the imperial family,

92
00:06:49,260 --> 00:06:50,450
while the other
is a high-ranking official.

93
00:06:50,450 --> 00:06:51,510
If they intervene,

94
00:06:51,710 --> 00:06:53,850
they can surely protect Ke
from suffering in prison.

95
00:06:53,850 --> 00:06:55,630
Okay. I'll go find Lord Xu.

96
00:06:55,650 --> 00:06:57,650
Then Chongshan and I will
go find Miss Cheng.

97
00:06:57,650 --> 00:06:58,890
I'll go prepare some money.

98
00:06:58,890 --> 00:07:00,390
Just let me handle the bribery matters.

99
00:07:00,390 --> 00:07:01,030
Okay.

100
00:07:01,050 --> 00:07:02,650
Lu Yi will protect Mr. and Mrs. Shi.

101
00:07:02,650 --> 00:07:04,080
If there's any news from Chief,

102
00:07:04,080 --> 00:07:05,450
I'll inform you all immediately.

103
00:07:05,450 --> 00:07:06,280
There's no time to waste.

104
00:07:06,280 --> 00:07:06,750
Let's go.

105
00:07:06,750 --> 00:07:07,310
Wait!

106
00:07:07,650 --> 00:07:09,600
There's something we still don't know yet.

107
00:07:09,600 --> 00:07:12,790
Who on earth did Ke offend?

108
00:07:14,040 --> 00:07:16,750
Ke has always been pure-hearted and kind
since childhood.

109
00:07:16,750 --> 00:07:18,350
She has made friends everywhere.

110
00:07:18,350 --> 00:07:19,500
How could she possibly offend anyone?

111
00:07:19,500 --> 00:07:20,350
Indeed.

112
00:07:20,390 --> 00:07:21,640
Ke is a helpful girl

113
00:07:21,700 --> 00:07:22,800
and is quite honey-tongued.

114
00:07:22,800 --> 00:07:24,400
How would she offend anyone?

115
00:07:25,150 --> 00:07:26,370
It's Marquis Wu'an.

116
00:07:27,360 --> 00:07:28,260
What?

117
00:07:28,830 --> 00:07:29,630
Previously,

118
00:07:29,750 --> 00:07:32,050
Marquis Wu'an pretended to be Mr. Lin Yuan
to get close to me.

119
00:07:32,050 --> 00:07:33,980
If Ke hadn't exposed him in time...

120
00:07:35,350 --> 00:07:37,990
Anyway,
in terms of having a grudge against Ke,

121
00:07:38,070 --> 00:07:39,450
he's the only person I can think of.

122
00:07:39,450 --> 00:07:41,210
The Military Headquarters
sent people here.

123
00:07:41,210 --> 00:07:42,950
It's probably him indeed.

124
00:07:43,830 --> 00:07:45,330
But we have no evidence.

125
00:07:46,370 --> 00:07:47,500
In that case,

126
00:07:47,670 --> 00:07:49,930
Ke once embarrassed Marquis Wu'an

127
00:07:50,140 --> 00:07:52,400
during Miss Cheng's matchmaking event.

128
00:07:52,460 --> 00:07:53,880
Then it's probably him indeed.

129
00:07:53,880 --> 00:07:55,740
But Marquis Wu'an has such a noble status

130
00:07:55,740 --> 00:07:57,159
and holds military power.

131
00:07:57,159 --> 00:07:58,409
If it's really him,

132
00:07:58,440 --> 00:07:59,700
what should we do then?

133
00:08:02,040 --> 00:08:02,820
Ke.

134
00:08:03,620 --> 00:08:05,950
I'll definitely find a way to protect you.

135
00:08:09,330 --> 00:08:11,630
Ke has been arrested by Marquis Wu'an.

136
00:08:11,850 --> 00:08:12,780
What did you say?

137
00:08:12,800 --> 00:08:13,980
Miss Cheng,

138
00:08:14,010 --> 00:08:15,080
we're still not quite clear

139
00:08:15,080 --> 00:08:16,590
about the reasons behind this.

140
00:08:16,590 --> 00:08:17,980
It's just our speculation.

141
00:08:17,980 --> 00:08:19,530
We need your help.

142
00:08:21,680 --> 00:08:22,890
[Petition]

143
00:08:24,250 --> 00:08:24,740
[Petition]

144
00:08:24,740 --> 00:08:25,340
Lord Xu.

145
00:08:25,950 --> 00:08:28,480
My sister
offended Marquis Wu'an previously.

146
00:08:28,480 --> 00:08:30,180
A few days ago, Marquis Wu'an asked people

147
00:08:30,180 --> 00:08:32,039
to arrest my sister for no reason.

148
00:08:32,330 --> 00:08:34,870
Now our Shi family is at our wits' end,

149
00:08:35,510 --> 00:08:37,510
so we would like to ask for your help.

150
00:08:38,240 --> 00:08:38,549
I have a petition here.

151
00:08:38,549 --> 00:08:40,789
[Petition]

152
00:08:41,390 --> 00:08:43,620
Lord Xu, please sign it

153
00:08:43,830 --> 00:08:44,790
to help us out.

154
00:08:53,310 --> 00:08:54,790
[Petition]

155
00:08:55,030 --> 00:08:56,770
What crimes did Ke commit?

156
00:08:57,200 --> 00:08:58,400
Yeah. Why did they arrest her?

157
00:08:58,400 --> 00:09:00,200
Is there any misunderstanding?

158
00:09:00,690 --> 00:09:02,350
Yeah. There must be a mistake.

159
00:09:02,370 --> 00:09:03,690
The Military Headquarters
arrested Ke for no reason.

160
00:09:03,690 --> 00:09:04,830
Everyone, please

161
00:09:04,860 --> 00:09:07,090
sign your names on this petition

162
00:09:07,120 --> 00:09:08,970
to intercede and vouch for Ke.

163
00:09:09,440 --> 00:09:10,300
I'll sign it first.

164
00:09:10,300 --> 00:09:12,320
I believe that Ke is innocent.

165
00:09:12,480 --> 00:09:13,320
I'll sign it, too.

166
00:09:13,320 --> 00:09:14,330
-I'll sign it, too.
-I'll sign it, too.

167
00:09:14,330 --> 00:09:16,390
-I'll sign it, too.
-I'll sign it, too.

168
00:09:16,390 --> 00:09:17,450
Thanks, everyone.

169
00:09:17,450 --> 00:09:19,280
Miss Yan, you and Ke just met each other.

170
00:09:19,280 --> 00:09:20,720
But you're running around
to help her like this.

171
00:09:20,720 --> 00:09:22,760
As her colleagues,
we should also do our best to help her.

172
00:09:22,760 --> 00:09:23,950
Besides the petition,

173
00:09:23,950 --> 00:09:25,790
if there's anything else we can help with,

174
00:09:25,790 --> 00:09:26,980
please don't hesitate to tell us.

175
00:09:26,980 --> 00:09:29,040
-We will do our best to help her.
-Yes.

176
00:09:30,800 --> 00:09:31,600
Thank you.

177
00:09:31,800 --> 00:09:33,000
I'm deeply grateful.

178
00:09:34,250 --> 00:09:35,080
-Let's go.
-Let's go.

179
00:09:35,080 --> 00:09:38,020
[Petition]

180
00:09:38,250 --> 00:09:40,650
[Zhao Gui]

181
00:09:40,650 --> 00:09:43,800
[Zhao Gui] [Meng] [Zhang Aizhen]

182
00:09:44,150 --> 00:09:45,230
[Liu Su]

183
00:09:45,700 --> 00:09:46,860
[Wu Qiuju]

184
00:09:47,040 --> 00:09:49,650
[Wu Qiuju, Li Meilian,
Liu Suhe, Meng Yan]

185
00:09:50,070 --> 00:09:51,690
[Petition]

186
00:09:55,390 --> 00:09:56,480
Guards!

187
00:09:57,390 --> 00:09:58,500
Didn't you say I'm guilty?

188
00:09:58,500 --> 00:10:00,700
Show me the evidence and put me on trial!

189
00:10:02,030 --> 00:10:04,160
The Military Headquarters
arrested innocent people arbitrarily.

190
00:10:04,160 --> 00:10:05,310
I'm innocent!

191
00:10:05,680 --> 00:10:07,160
I demand a joint trial
by the three judicial offices.

192
00:10:07,160 --> 00:10:08,300
I want a confrontation in court!

193
00:10:08,300 --> 00:10:09,580
I'll file an appeal to His Majesty!

194
00:10:09,580 --> 00:10:11,220
Come here! Did you hear me?

195
00:10:12,010 --> 00:10:12,940
Shi Fa'ke.

196
00:10:16,520 --> 00:10:18,230
You're quite energetic.

197
00:10:19,730 --> 00:10:20,980
It's really you, Lord Marquis.

198
00:10:20,980 --> 00:10:22,250
I knew it was you.

199
00:10:23,820 --> 00:10:25,050
Keeping you alive until today

200
00:10:25,050 --> 00:10:26,910
is already an act of mercy from me.

201
00:10:27,620 --> 00:10:29,930
Now your dear Lu

202
00:10:30,060 --> 00:10:31,690
has already arrived at Mount Qianya.

203
00:10:31,690 --> 00:10:35,680
I wonder how he feels now
after seeing that

204
00:10:36,600 --> 00:10:38,930
Mount Qianya had been razed to the ground.

205
00:10:39,450 --> 00:10:41,250
Lord Marquis, aren't you afraid

206
00:10:41,530 --> 00:10:43,140
His Majesty will find out
about your private army?

207
00:10:43,140 --> 00:10:44,030
His Majesty?

208
00:10:47,540 --> 00:10:49,990
He can barely protect himself now.

209
00:10:52,920 --> 00:10:53,950
Let me tell you.

210
00:10:54,270 --> 00:10:56,590
All those who go against me

211
00:10:56,620 --> 00:10:58,580
will have to pay the price.

212
00:10:58,740 --> 00:11:00,740
You're being overconfident, Lord Marquis.

213
00:11:00,740 --> 00:11:01,870
Fate has its own way.

214
00:11:01,980 --> 00:11:04,290
Aren't you afraid of becoming the mantis

215
00:11:04,380 --> 00:11:06,090
that gets caught by the sparrow?

216
00:11:06,090 --> 00:11:08,800
Fine. Then I'll keep you alive
for a few more days.

217
00:11:08,800 --> 00:11:09,800
I'll show you

218
00:11:09,950 --> 00:11:11,710
who is the real sparrow.

219
00:11:12,530 --> 00:11:14,350
Lu left the capital at this time.

220
00:11:14,430 --> 00:11:16,590
I'm sure
he has made thorough preparations.

221
00:11:16,590 --> 00:11:17,390
Lord Marquis,

222
00:11:17,640 --> 00:11:19,400
I advise you to start thinking about

223
00:11:19,400 --> 00:11:20,830
your own escape plan.

224
00:11:23,920 --> 00:11:25,350
I'd like to see

225
00:11:25,470 --> 00:11:27,960
whether Lu will come back to save you

226
00:11:28,820 --> 00:11:31,120
or stay there to defend Mount Qianya,

227
00:11:31,230 --> 00:11:33,530
which is the Emperor's last refuge.

228
00:11:39,400 --> 00:11:40,440
Lord Marquis.

229
00:11:40,520 --> 00:11:42,450
Perhaps Lu will come to

230
00:11:42,530 --> 00:11:43,860
your room soon

231
00:11:44,060 --> 00:11:45,040
and then...

232
00:11:45,550 --> 00:11:47,080
How dare you talk like that?

233
00:11:50,300 --> 00:11:51,000
Alright.

234
00:11:51,850 --> 00:11:53,140
Then you can stay here

235
00:11:53,420 --> 00:11:56,600
and wait to be reunited with Lu's corpse.

236
00:11:56,860 --> 00:11:57,270
Let's go!

237
00:11:57,270 --> 00:11:57,790
You...

238
00:11:58,920 --> 00:11:59,980
Don't leave!

239
00:12:00,030 --> 00:12:00,890
Come back!

240
00:12:03,150 --> 00:12:06,190
Marquis Wu'an
is actually plotting to usurp the throne.

241
00:12:06,190 --> 00:12:07,820
Will Lu be in danger?

242
00:12:13,370 --> 00:12:14,190
Chi.

243
00:12:14,440 --> 00:12:16,890
Although we've caused heavy damage
to the enemy's vanguard,

244
00:12:16,890 --> 00:12:18,620
we're still outnumbered by them.

245
00:12:18,620 --> 00:12:19,770
If they don't retreat,

246
00:12:19,770 --> 00:12:21,570
we'll have no chance of winning.

247
00:12:21,920 --> 00:12:23,550
If we still don't request reinforcements,

248
00:12:23,550 --> 00:12:24,970
I'm afraid
we won't be able to defend Mount Qianya.

249
00:12:24,970 --> 00:12:25,580
We can't do that.

250
00:12:25,580 --> 00:12:26,640
If we do that,

251
00:12:26,850 --> 00:12:28,980
we'll fall into Marquis Wu'an's trap.

252
00:12:29,860 --> 00:12:31,280
If His Majesty sends troops
to reinforce us,

253
00:12:31,280 --> 00:12:32,940
there won't be enough troops
in the palace.

254
00:12:32,940 --> 00:12:35,070
We can't request reinforcements now.

255
00:12:38,320 --> 00:12:40,650
Master, here's a letter from the capital.

256
00:12:43,390 --> 00:12:45,210
Marquis Wu'an has arrested Shi Fa'ke
to take her hostage.

257
00:12:45,210 --> 00:12:47,470
Return to the capital at once to save her.

258
00:12:55,310 --> 00:12:56,810
Marquis Wu'an

259
00:12:56,830 --> 00:12:58,150
actually arrested Ke while you were not

260
00:12:58,150 --> 00:12:59,640
in the capital.

261
00:12:59,810 --> 00:13:01,070
Chi, what should we do?

262
00:13:01,100 --> 00:13:02,240
Why don't we go back now

263
00:13:02,240 --> 00:13:03,100
to save Ke?

264
00:13:04,240 --> 00:13:04,890
No.

265
00:13:06,740 --> 00:13:08,150
I cannot go back now.

266
00:13:09,420 --> 00:13:11,300
Marquis Wu'an has taken Ke hostage,

267
00:13:11,300 --> 00:13:12,630
firstly to threaten me,

268
00:13:12,960 --> 00:13:13,690
and secondly, to lure me out of here

269
00:13:13,690 --> 00:13:15,550
to break apart Mount Qianya's forces.

270
00:13:15,550 --> 00:13:17,080
If I leave Mount Qianya now,

271
00:13:17,630 --> 00:13:19,010
then Ke will no longer

272
00:13:19,040 --> 00:13:20,570
be useful to Marquis Wu'an.

273
00:13:21,170 --> 00:13:22,870
Then it'll be truly dangerous.

274
00:13:22,870 --> 00:13:24,740
But Chi, if you don't go back,

