548
00:26:30,750 --> 00:26:31,480
-Leave!
-Ke.

549
00:26:31,550 --> 00:26:32,500
Just leave!

550
00:26:32,520 --> 00:26:33,380
Ke, listen to me!

551
00:26:33,380 --> 00:26:34,380
-Let go of me!
-Ke!

552
00:26:38,810 --> 00:26:40,270
Beware of eavesdroppers.

553
00:26:41,650 --> 00:26:42,340
What?

554
00:26:42,920 --> 00:26:44,330
Lu Chi.

555
00:26:48,660 --> 00:26:50,460
I want you to do me a favor, Mr. He.

556
00:26:51,110 --> 00:26:52,530
What makes you think I'll agree?

557
00:26:52,530 --> 00:26:54,660
I can ask no one but you to do this favor.

558
00:26:54,990 --> 00:26:56,080
It's about Ke.

559
00:26:56,940 --> 00:26:57,620
What is it?

560
00:26:58,200 --> 00:26:59,820
After I returned to Mount Qianya,

561
00:26:59,820 --> 00:27:01,750
Ke has been targeted by Marquis Wu'an.

562
00:27:01,750 --> 00:27:02,750
If he's in a desperate situation,

563
00:27:02,750 --> 00:27:04,130
no one knows what he might do.

564
00:27:04,130 --> 00:27:06,720
Please take care of Ke for me

565
00:27:07,090 --> 00:27:08,170
and protect her.

566
00:27:10,660 --> 00:27:11,990
You don't need to ask me to do that.

567
00:27:11,990 --> 00:27:13,790
I'll certainly take care of her.

568
00:27:16,770 --> 00:27:17,700
In times of danger,

569
00:27:17,700 --> 00:27:20,200
just tell them
I'll lead troops to attack the capital

570
00:27:20,200 --> 00:27:22,130
for the purpose of keeping Ke safe.

571
00:27:24,980 --> 00:27:27,440
Lu Chi will bring troops
back to the capital.

572
00:27:28,720 --> 00:27:30,520
Then what should we do now?

573
00:27:30,810 --> 00:27:31,720
Speak louder.

574
00:27:32,810 --> 00:27:33,700
Speak louder.

575
00:27:36,740 --> 00:27:37,840
If you work for Marquis Wu'an,

576
00:27:37,840 --> 00:27:39,010
you won't end up well.

577
00:27:39,010 --> 00:27:40,080
Lu will soon

578
00:27:40,100 --> 00:27:41,690
lead his troops to attack the city.

579
00:27:41,690 --> 00:27:43,410
Then Marquis Wu'an will be beheaded.

580
00:27:43,410 --> 00:27:44,600
You won't end up well, either.

581
00:27:44,600 --> 00:27:46,700
Ke, don't be so stubborn.

582
00:27:46,980 --> 00:27:49,080
Lu Chi can barely protect himself now.

583
00:27:49,080 --> 00:27:51,010
Marquis Wu'an is destined to be the ruler.

584
00:27:51,010 --> 00:27:52,620
I think you've lost your mind.

585
00:27:52,620 --> 00:27:55,940
Shi Fa'ke is indeed feisty.

586
00:27:56,100 --> 00:27:57,340
I really don't understand

587
00:27:57,340 --> 00:28:00,800
why Lu Chi and He Kexian like her so much.

588
00:28:01,110 --> 00:28:02,030
I don't want to hear it.

589
00:28:02,030 --> 00:28:02,670
Get lost!

590
00:28:02,720 --> 00:28:04,110
I don't want to see you again.

591
00:28:04,110 --> 00:28:05,200
As long as you do as I say,

592
00:28:05,200 --> 00:28:06,190
I can let you out.

593
00:28:06,350 --> 00:28:07,280
Dream on.

594
00:28:07,830 --> 00:28:09,030
Lu will soon come here

595
00:28:09,160 --> 00:28:10,370
to save me.

596
00:28:33,310 --> 00:28:34,440
Greetings, My Lord.

597
00:28:35,500 --> 00:28:36,500
Mr. He.

598
00:28:36,590 --> 00:28:38,450
Have you seen your beloved woman?

599
00:28:38,830 --> 00:28:39,600
Yes, I have.

600
00:28:40,030 --> 00:28:41,630
Thanks for your help, My Lord.

601
00:28:41,630 --> 00:28:43,160
But Ke is still young.

602
00:28:43,270 --> 00:28:46,070
It may take some time for her
to accept this matter.

603
00:28:46,370 --> 00:28:47,590
But don't worry, My Lord.

604
00:28:47,590 --> 00:28:49,720
I will certainly persuade her properly.

605
00:28:49,720 --> 00:28:51,070
Oh, by the way, Ke has said that

606
00:28:51,070 --> 00:28:53,070
Lu Chi will come to attack the city soon.

607
00:28:53,070 --> 00:28:54,670
Please be prepared, My Lord.

608
00:28:55,110 --> 00:28:55,660
Okay.

609
00:28:57,400 --> 00:29:00,200
I'm aware of your kindness.

610
00:29:00,270 --> 00:29:01,450
Don't worry.

611
00:29:01,830 --> 00:29:03,400
Once Lu Chi dies,

612
00:29:03,590 --> 00:29:06,740
you'll surely be able to marry that woman.

613
00:29:07,830 --> 00:29:09,760
Thanks for your auspicious words.

614
00:29:16,340 --> 00:29:17,590
-Open the door!
-Open the door!

615
00:29:17,590 --> 00:29:18,480
Open the door!

616
00:29:20,110 --> 00:29:22,310
The shop is closed today. Please leave.

617
00:29:26,640 --> 00:29:27,620
We're here to take over He's Bakery.

618
00:29:27,620 --> 00:29:28,750
[Official Deed]

619
00:29:29,440 --> 00:29:31,650
Now this shop belongs to Lord Marquis.

620
00:29:31,680 --> 00:29:32,370
Well...

621
00:29:32,690 --> 00:29:32,790
How is that possible?

622
00:29:32,790 --> 00:29:33,270
[Official Deed]

623
00:29:33,300 --> 00:29:35,320
[Assignor: He Shiyuan,
Assignee: He Kexian]

624
00:29:35,350 --> 00:29:37,260
This title deed must be fake!

625
00:29:37,330 --> 00:29:37,400
[Official Deed]

626
00:29:37,400 --> 00:29:38,380
How dare you!

627
00:29:38,480 --> 00:29:40,190
How could you slander Lord Marquis?

628
00:29:40,190 --> 00:29:41,850
Mr. He personally gave this title deed
to Lord Marquis

629
00:29:41,850 --> 00:29:42,830
as a token of his loyalty.

630
00:29:42,830 --> 00:29:44,470
Being able to work for Lord Marquis

631
00:29:44,470 --> 00:29:45,750
is the He family's honor.

632
00:29:45,750 --> 00:29:46,830
That's impossible.

633
00:29:46,830 --> 00:29:49,110
How would my brother
side with Marquis Wu'an?

634
00:29:49,110 --> 00:29:50,030
Whether you believe it or not,
it's not up to you.

635
00:29:50,030 --> 00:29:50,660
Leave now!

636
00:29:50,690 --> 00:29:52,400
-Just leave!
-What are you doing? Let go of me!

637
00:29:52,400 --> 00:29:52,800
Leave now!

638
00:29:52,800 --> 00:29:53,550
Get out of my shop! Leave at once!

639
00:29:53,550 --> 00:29:55,080
-Leave now!
-Leave at once!

640
00:29:55,200 --> 00:29:56,130
Are you alright?

641
00:29:56,360 --> 00:29:57,220
Chongshan.

642
00:29:57,250 --> 00:29:58,730
They said my brother had given this shop

643
00:29:58,730 --> 00:29:59,930
to Marquis Wu'an.

644
00:30:06,240 --> 00:30:07,160
Don't confront them directly.

645
00:30:07,160 --> 00:30:09,270
Let's leave first and figure things out.

646
00:30:09,270 --> 00:30:10,010
Let's go.

647
00:30:12,860 --> 00:30:15,660
This is not okay.
I need to get to the bottom of this.

648
00:30:15,750 --> 00:30:16,680
Ketian! Ketian!

649
00:30:16,720 --> 00:30:18,520
Chongshan, why are you stopping me?

650
00:30:18,520 --> 00:30:20,010
You need to trust Kexian.

651
00:30:20,240 --> 00:30:21,360
Since he has done this,

652
00:30:21,360 --> 00:30:22,940
he must have his own reasons.

653
00:30:22,940 --> 00:30:24,650
Of course I trust my brother.

654
00:30:24,720 --> 00:30:26,070
As I trust him,

655
00:30:26,070 --> 00:30:26,970
I know

656
00:30:26,990 --> 00:30:29,000
he would never side with Marquis Wu'an.

657
00:30:29,000 --> 00:30:30,210
I need to get to the bottom of this.

658
00:30:30,210 --> 00:30:31,770
No, Ketian.

659
00:30:31,960 --> 00:30:33,520
Give Kexian some time.

660
00:30:34,140 --> 00:30:35,180
Trust me.

661
00:30:35,550 --> 00:30:38,020
If you go in there now,
it won't be helpful.

662
00:30:40,590 --> 00:30:41,480
Ketian.

663
00:30:46,070 --> 00:30:46,510
Let's go.

664
00:30:46,510 --> 00:30:52,660
[He's Bakery]

665
00:30:58,670 --> 00:30:59,610
Step aside!

666
00:31:01,420 --> 00:31:04,150
Are they my father's men?

667
00:31:05,110 --> 00:31:06,480
That's her.

668
00:31:16,400 --> 00:31:18,970
No, these aren't my father's men.

669
00:31:19,590 --> 00:31:20,520
Let's chase her!

670
00:31:21,160 --> 00:31:21,950
Hurry!

671
00:31:23,250 --> 00:31:24,120
Hurry up!

672
00:31:36,590 --> 00:31:37,510
Mr. Huang!

673
00:31:39,510 --> 00:31:40,200
Where is she?

674
00:31:40,200 --> 00:31:40,900
Hurry!

675
00:32:06,550 --> 00:32:07,750
Thank you, Mr. Huang.

676
00:32:24,920 --> 00:32:25,720
Lord Marquis!

677
00:32:25,830 --> 00:32:26,630
Lord Marquis!

678
00:32:27,270 --> 00:32:28,550
A confidential letter.

679
00:32:28,550 --> 00:32:29,110
Hurry!

680
00:32:31,590 --> 00:32:32,960
[Chi is dead.]

681
00:32:34,400 --> 00:32:35,510
Lord Marquis, there's more.

682
00:32:35,510 --> 00:32:37,570
This is Lu Chi's personal belonging.

683
00:32:40,600 --> 00:32:42,020
[Shi Fa'ke]

684
00:32:45,470 --> 00:32:47,310
Heaven is truly helping me.

685
00:32:47,530 --> 00:32:49,060
Heaven is helping me!

686
00:32:50,680 --> 00:32:51,600
Let me ask you.

687
00:32:51,710 --> 00:32:53,830
Is there any news from the palace lately?

688
00:32:53,830 --> 00:32:54,720
My Lord,

689
00:32:54,790 --> 00:32:57,240
there has been no movement
from that person lately.

690
00:32:57,240 --> 00:33:00,370
I've heard he's often missing
from his bedchamber, too.

691
00:33:00,680 --> 00:33:02,980
I think he probably knows that

692
00:33:03,050 --> 00:33:04,240
his good fortune has run out,

693
00:33:04,240 --> 00:33:06,280
so he has escaped first to survive.

694
00:33:07,000 --> 00:33:09,030
In that case, what are we waiting for?

695
00:33:09,030 --> 00:33:10,380
Pass my order.

696
00:33:11,320 --> 00:33:11,530
Get ready to enter the palace.

697
00:33:11,530 --> 00:33:13,180
[Chi is dead.]

698
00:33:21,190 --> 00:33:22,070
[Marriage]

699
00:33:22,070 --> 00:33:24,780
We'll have to make do with
staying here tonight.

700
00:33:28,640 --> 00:33:30,070
Actually, I think

701
00:33:30,310 --> 00:33:31,880
the condition here is too bad for you.

702
00:33:31,880 --> 00:33:33,400
How about I walk around to see

703
00:33:33,400 --> 00:33:35,190
if there's a farmhouse
where we could stay?

704
00:33:35,190 --> 00:33:35,880
No need.

705
00:33:37,680 --> 00:33:39,780
I think this place is fine.

706
00:33:39,880 --> 00:33:41,610
There's fire to keep us warm.

707
00:33:42,070 --> 00:33:42,960
Also,

708
00:33:44,590 --> 00:33:46,120
you're here to talk with me.

709
00:33:49,880 --> 00:33:50,490
By the way,

710
00:33:50,590 --> 00:33:53,300
you saved me again today.

711
00:33:53,580 --> 00:33:54,380
Thank you.

712
00:33:54,790 --> 00:33:56,520
Miss Qiyue, no need to thank me.

713
00:33:57,620 --> 00:34:00,110
[Marriage]

714
00:34:02,170 --> 00:34:04,400
[Marriage]

715
00:34:10,540 --> 00:34:12,139
What are you thinking about?

716
00:34:12,880 --> 00:34:13,880
I'm thinking that

717
00:34:15,030 --> 00:34:17,590
actually, we are destined
to meet each other often.

718
00:34:17,590 --> 00:34:17,889
We met each other unexpectedly
again and again.

719
00:34:17,889 --> 00:34:19,440
[Marriage]

720
00:34:19,440 --> 00:34:21,840
And we managed to
escape danger every time.

721
00:34:23,840 --> 00:34:26,600
Miss Qiyue, your every twinkle and smile

722
00:34:26,760 --> 00:34:28,460
have always been in my mind.

723
00:34:30,400 --> 00:34:32,360
Actually, I want to tell you that...

724
00:34:32,360 --> 00:34:34,400
However, what if one day,

725
00:34:34,960 --> 00:34:36,670
you discover that the person you know

726
00:34:36,670 --> 00:34:38,080
isn't the real me,

727
00:34:38,400 --> 00:34:39,190
but someone else?

728
00:34:39,190 --> 00:34:40,370
What would you do?

729
00:34:46,219 --> 00:34:47,580
What if one day,

730
00:34:47,630 --> 00:34:49,320
you discover that the person you know

731
00:34:49,320 --> 00:34:50,800
isn't the real me, either?

732
00:34:51,070 --> 00:34:52,110
What would you do?

733
00:34:57,920 --> 00:34:59,250
I asked you first.

734
00:34:59,250 --> 00:35:02,310
[Marriage]

735
00:35:02,310 --> 00:35:03,440
Then let me tell you.

736
00:35:04,120 --> 00:35:06,720
No matter who I am and who you are,

737
00:35:06,800 --> 00:35:08,060
to me,

738
00:35:08,240 --> 00:35:09,900
you will always be Miss Qiyue.

739
00:35:16,510 --> 00:35:19,010
It's all my fault for implicating you.

740
00:35:19,030 --> 00:35:19,970
Otherwise,

741
00:35:20,070 --> 00:35:22,110
you wouldn't need to
be in this awful place.

742
00:35:22,110 --> 00:35:23,960
But I'm willing to be implicated by you.

743
00:35:23,960 --> 00:35:25,000
What did you say?

744
00:35:27,480 --> 00:35:28,760
I said...

745
00:35:29,090 --> 00:35:30,900
Actually, I think this place

746
00:35:30,930 --> 00:35:32,000
is quite nice.

747
00:35:32,230 --> 00:35:34,150
It's quiet and relaxing.

748
00:35:34,280 --> 00:35:35,250
Oh, by the way,

749
00:35:35,400 --> 00:35:36,510
I forgot to ask you.

750
00:35:36,630 --> 00:35:37,880
Why did those thugs

751
00:35:37,900 --> 00:35:39,500
keep chasing you today?

752
00:35:44,440 --> 00:35:45,760
To be honest with you,

753
00:35:45,760 --> 00:35:48,710
I actually ran away from home.

754
00:35:48,710 --> 00:35:49,960
You ran away?

755
00:35:52,150 --> 00:35:53,800
I didn't want an arranged marriage,

756
00:35:53,800 --> 00:35:56,330
so I ran away from home.

757
00:35:56,440 --> 00:35:57,760
Then I met Ke,

758
00:35:57,780 --> 00:35:58,780
and she took me in.

759
00:36:00,190 --> 00:36:01,110
Do you think...

760
00:36:01,150 --> 00:36:02,460
No, Miss Qiyue.

761
00:36:02,630 --> 00:36:04,760
I think we have even more in common now.

762
00:36:04,920 --> 00:36:06,430
I ran away from home, too.

763
00:36:06,730 --> 00:36:08,730
Really? You also escaped marriage?

764
00:36:08,840 --> 00:36:12,900
My situation is actually more complicated
than just escaping marriage.

765
00:36:15,920 --> 00:36:16,800
However,

766
00:36:16,920 --> 00:36:19,070
Ke once told me something.

767
00:36:20,150 --> 00:36:21,710
Not marrying someone you love

768
00:36:21,710 --> 00:36:23,280
will never bring happiness.

769
00:36:23,280 --> 00:36:24,080
So,

770
00:36:25,190 --> 00:36:26,920
I think you did the right thing.

771
00:36:31,030 --> 00:36:35,080
I once saw a painting by Mr. Lin Yuan.

772
00:36:35,360 --> 00:36:36,820
There are such words in it.

773
00:36:37,520 --> 00:36:39,970
May I be like a star
and you be like the moon.

774
00:36:40,460 --> 00:36:43,580
Then we can shine together every night.

775
00:36:45,490 --> 00:36:47,670
Do you know what those words mean?

776
00:36:50,760 --> 00:36:51,760
I think I do.

777
00:36:51,760 --> 00:36:53,620
Meeting you deepens my feelings.

778
00:36:54,880 --> 00:36:56,940
I only regret not meeting you sooner.

779
00:37:01,070 --> 00:37:05,020
I'll go gather some more firewood.

780
00:37:05,960 --> 00:37:06,960
I'll go with you.

781
00:37:23,140 --> 00:37:24,340
Marriage Broker Shi.

782
00:37:24,590 --> 00:37:26,070
How have you been lately?

783
00:37:26,320 --> 00:37:28,920
I asked people to take good care of you.

784
00:37:30,670 --> 00:37:33,850
May I ask what brings you here today?

785
00:37:35,400 --> 00:37:36,630
I'm here today

786
00:37:36,880 --> 00:37:39,630
to tell you something very important.

787
00:37:40,150 --> 00:37:42,710
And it's good news.

788
00:37:44,670 --> 00:37:45,920
Good news?

789
00:37:52,140 --> 00:37:53,310
[Shi Fa'ke]

790
00:37:53,310 --> 00:37:54,600
Look carefully.

791
00:38:01,300 --> 00:38:02,020
This...

792
00:38:03,270 --> 00:38:05,560
is the seal Lu carved for me.

793
00:38:06,360 --> 00:38:07,630
So you can recognize it?

794
00:38:07,630 --> 00:38:08,960
I'm here to tell you that

795
00:38:09,450 --> 00:38:11,110
your dear Lu Chi

796
00:38:11,520 --> 00:38:12,680
is dead.

797
00:38:16,960 --> 00:38:17,690
Don't you think

798
00:38:17,690 --> 00:38:20,470
this is wonderful news?

799
00:38:24,810 --> 00:38:25,940
That's impossible.

800
00:38:26,960 --> 00:38:28,150
Stop lying to me!

801
00:38:28,360 --> 00:38:29,430
This seal

802
00:38:29,480 --> 00:38:32,220
was found on Lu Chi's corpse.

803
00:38:32,710 --> 00:38:34,310
There's no falsehood at all.

804
00:38:36,640 --> 00:38:39,570
Among all those items
that could prove his identity,

805
00:38:39,660 --> 00:38:42,030
Lu only left this seal.

806
00:38:42,370 --> 00:38:43,900
Could it be that he isn't...

807
00:38:45,290 --> 00:38:47,150
Lu must be safe now.

808
00:38:47,280 --> 00:38:50,450
The seal is just a strategy
to deceive Marquis Wu'an.

809
00:38:51,210 --> 00:38:53,140
I can't let Marquis Wu'an find out.

810
00:38:56,790 --> 00:38:57,990
Marriage Broker Shi.

811
00:38:58,800 --> 00:39:00,060
My condolences.

812
00:39:00,810 --> 00:39:03,910
I've noticed that Mr. He loves you deeply.

813
00:39:05,680 --> 00:39:07,010
You can think about him.

814
00:39:11,440 --> 00:39:12,220
Get out.

815
00:39:12,760 --> 00:39:13,810
Get out!

816
00:39:18,550 --> 00:39:19,650
Belive it or not,

817
00:39:19,680 --> 00:39:21,100
I could kill you now

818
00:39:21,110 --> 00:39:23,230
so that you could
join Lu Chi in the netherworld.

819
00:39:23,230 --> 00:39:24,230
You won't do that.

820
00:39:26,670 --> 00:39:28,230
You're indeed quite clever.

821
00:39:28,230 --> 00:39:29,810
You know I won't kill you,

822
00:39:29,960 --> 00:39:31,360
as you're still useful to me.

823
00:39:31,360 --> 00:39:33,920
So take good care of yourself.

824
00:39:34,000 --> 00:39:37,180
Don't forget
you still have parents and brothers.

825
00:40:12,610 --> 00:40:15,670
Qiyue, wait for me to come back.

826
00:40:33,900 --> 00:40:35,550
[Zhaoyang Gate]

827
00:40:42,090 --> 00:40:44,930
[Zhaoyang Gate]

